text: Tarik Biberović (born 28 January 2001)) is a Bosnian-Turkish professional basketball player for Fenerbahçe of the Turkish Basketball Super League and the EuroLeague. He can play at the point guard and small forward positions. ==Personal life== Biberović was born in Zenica, Bosnia and Herzegovina. ==References== Category:2001 births Category:Living people Category:Fenerbahçe men's basketball players Category:Sportspeople from Zenica Category:Turkish basketball players Category:Small forwards Category:Point guards
